<div id="modal-profile-pic" class="modal hide fade modal-share-msgs" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
	
	<div class="auto-size-block modal-content">
		
		<h2 class="font-title">Escolher <strong>Foto de Perfil</strong></h2>
		
		<h4 class="header-base-title">Modelo: <strong><%= @model.name %></strong></h4>
		
		<div class="modal-alert">
			<p>Por favor, fa√ßa o upload dos arquivos antes de escolher a foto de perfil.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div id="profile-pic-preview">
			
			<input type="hidden" value="" id="original-img-w">
			<input type="hidden" value="" id="original-img-h">
			
			<div id="profile-pic-original" class="put-left">
				<p>Imagem original aqui</p>
			</div>
			
			<div id="profile-pic-thumb" class="put-left">
				<p>Imagem preview aqui</p>
			</div>
			
		</div>
		
		<div class="content-split"></div>
		
		<div id="profile-pic-list" class="auto-size-block">
			<p>Selecione a imagem desejada na lista abaixo:</p>
			<ul class="put-list-inline">
				<% for photo in @model.photos.each %>

					<li class="is-draggable ui-widget-content ui-corner-tr">
					<%= image_tag photo.image.url(:main_composite), alt: photo.image_file_name, id: photo.id %>
					</li>

				<% end %>
			</ul>
		</div>
		
		<div class="modal-btn-action">
			<%= link_to "SALVAR", "#", :class => "anchor-btn-gold-light-4-column" %>
		</div>
		
	</div>
	
</div>